'''德源隱修院'''是屬[[天主教|天主教]][[本篤會|本篤會]][[聖奧提來本篤會|聖奧提來會]]的一所[[修道院|修道院]]，位於現今[[北韓|北韓]][[江原道_(朝鮮)|江原道]]首府[[元山市|元山市]]附近。修道院原來是[[漢城|漢城]]（今首爾）的傳教修士團，於1920年代遷至德源，接管新成立的[[天主教咸興教區|元山宗座代牧區]]。由於朝鮮自1949年對[[基督徒|基督徒]]施以迫害<ref>{{cite web |title = North Korean Martyrs, the first process for beatification gets underway |work = Asia News, May 25, 2007 |url = http://www.asianews.it/index.php?l=en&art=9368 |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |archive-date = 2012-09-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120925222950/http://www.asianews.it/index.php?l=en&art=9368 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，使當地教會活動停止<ref name="#1">{{cite web |title = Diocesan Directory: Territorial Abbacy of Tokwon |work = UCA News, August 2, 2006 |url = http://www.ucanews.com/diocesan-directory/html/dps-ko_tokwon.php |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120418012622/http://www.ucanews.com/diocesan-directory/html/dps-ko_tokwon.php |archivedate = 2012年4月18日 }}</ref>。但是德源自治會院區形式上仍然被列為[[天主教會|天主教會]]目前僅存的[[自治會院區|自治會院區]]之一<ref>{{cite web |title = Catholic Dioceses in the World by Type: Territorial Abbacies |work = Giga-Catholic Information, January 14, 2012 |url = http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/data/type-abby.htm |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |archive-date = 2013-01-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130119154220/http://gcatholic.org/dioceses/data/type-abby.htm }}</ref>。

==建立 ==
1909年2月，聖奧提來會的[[德國|德籍]]修士抵達漢城。他們沿襲在非洲會院的模式，修士開設了木匠工房和技藝學校，而司鐸們就埋首於牧民和教育工作。隨著更多的修士自歐洲抵達，修道院在1913年5月15日升格為院牧級隱修院。波尼法爵‧蘇爾神父獲委任為首任院牧<ref>{{cite book |last = Sieber, OSB |first = Godfrey |title = The Benedictine Congregation of St. Ottilien |year = 1992 |publisher = EOS Verlag |location = St Ottilien |isbn = 3-88096-645-1 |pages = 35}}</ref>。

1920年元山宗座代牧區自漢城宗座代牧區分出，由聖本篤隱修院的修士們接管。1927年漢城的會院關閉，大約四十名修士遷至德源。1927至28年間，興建了培養本土教區司鐸的小修院和大修院。一座[[羅曼復興式建築|羅曼復興式]]聖堂在1929年至31年間興建<ref name="#2">{{cite web |title = The Martyrs of Tokwon: Biographies (1-part) |work = Missionary Benedictines of St. Ottilien, June 10, 2011 |url = http://www.missionsbenediktiner.de/seligsprechung/cms/kategorie/index.php?kategorieid=61&parentid=61&languageid=1 |accessdate= January 19, 2012}}</ref>。大概在這個時候，修道院也開始培育本土的修道[[聖召|聖召]]。

1940年教宗[[庇護十二世|庇護十二世]]發出''Libenter Romanus Pontifex''[[教宗詔書|詔書]]，德源自治會院區成立，幅員包括元山、[[文川市|文川]]、[[安邊郡|安邊]]、[[川內郡|川內]]、[[高原郡|高原]]等地。蘇爾院牧成為了自治會院區的教長，並兼任咸興宗座代牧區的宗座署理<ref name="bolla">{{cite journal
|journal = [[宗座公報|宗座公報]]
|publisher = 梵蒂岡出版社
|date = 1940年
|volume = 32
|title = ''Libenter Romanus Pontifex''
|page = 343
|url = http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2032%20%5B1940%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|access-date = 2013-04-30
|archive-date = 2010-03-27
|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100327070022/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2032%20%5B1940%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|dead-url = no
}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>。[[二戰|二戰]]結束時，隱修院落入蘇聯軍隊手上。雖然修道院一度成為軍營，但修道生活還是逐漸恢復過來了<ref>{{cite book |last = Sieber, OSB |title = The Benedictine Congregation|pages=37}}</ref>。在1949年蘇軍撤走前，修道院有大約六十名修士，其中廿五名是國籍修士<ref>{{cite book |last = Sieber, OSB |title = The Benedictine Congregation |pages = 38}}</ref>，另外在元山有大約二十名圖欽格會修女<ref name="#3">{{cite web |title = The Martyrs of Tokwon: Historical Preliminary Notes |work = Missionary Benedictines of St. Ottilien, June 10, 2011 |url = http://www.missionsbenediktiner.de/seligsprechung/cms/kategorie/index.php?kategorieid=59&parentid=59&languageid=1 |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |archive-date = 2014-10-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141017162850/http://www.missionsbenediktiner.de/seligsprechung/cms/kategorie/index.php?kategorieid=59&parentid=59&languageid=1 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==教難==
1949年5月，朝鮮[[國家安全保衛部|國家安全保衛部]]佔領了修道院，拘捕了所有修士、修女，把他們移送了監獄和[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国集中营|集中營]]<ref name="#3"/>。1950年7月，[[朝鮮人民軍|朝鮮人民軍]]摧毀了修道院<ref>{{cite web |title = Destroyed Church in Wonsan Vicinity |work = Willibroard’s Gallery |url = http://picasaweb.google.com/WillibrordDriever/TokwonAbteikircheNachDerZerstorung#5318714733524560162 |accessdate = January 10, 2012 |archive-date = 2012-07-18 |archive-url = https://archive.today/20120718033834/http://picasaweb.google.com/WillibrordDriever/TokwonAbteikircheNachDerZerstorung%235318714733524560162#5318714733524560162 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。1949年至52年間十四名修士和兩名修女在經歷嚴酷的囚禁和虐待後被處決<ref>{{cite web |title = The Martyrs of Tokwon: Biographies (2-part) |work = Missionary Benedictines of St. Ottilien, June 10, 2011 |url = http://www.missionsbenediktiner.de/seligsprechung/cms/kategorie/index.php?kategorieid=64&parentid=64&languageid=1 |accessdate = January 19, 2012}}</ref>。同時十七名修士和兩名修女因飢饉、疾病、若役和集中營的惡劣環境死去<ref>{{cite web |title = The Martyrs of Tokwon: A Chronology of the Martyrdoms (German) |work = Missionary Benedictines of St. Ottilien, June 10, 2011 |url = http://www.missionsbenediktiner.de/seligsprechung/cms/kategorie/index.php?kategorieid=10&languageid=1 |accessdate= January 19, 2012}}</ref>。1950年2月1日蘇爾院牧死於[[平壤|平壤]]的一所監獄，同年10月所有高級修士被處決<ref name="#2"/>。1954年1月，倖存的四十二名德國修士、修女經[[西伯利亞鐵路|西伯利亞鐵路]]被遣送回德國<ref name="#1"/>。

[[2007年5月|2007年5月]]開啟了把德源隱修院36名在[[金日成|金日成]]治下反教會迫害中[[殉道|殉道]]的“[[天主之僕|天主之僕]]”冊封為[[真福品|真福品]]的程序。程序標題為「波尼法爵‧蘇爾神父 O.S.B.、金本篤 O.S.B.及其同伴列為真福品案」<ref>{{cite web |title = N. Korea martyrs slated for sainthood |work = Religion and Spirituality, May 28, 2007 |url = http://www.religionandspirituality.com/view/post/11803293318500/N_Korea_martyrs_slated_for_sainthood/ |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130314041217/http://www.religionandspirituality.com/view/post/11803293318500/N_Korea_martyrs_slated_for_sainthood/ |archivedate = 2013年3月14日 }}</ref>。

== 現狀 ==
德源隱修院的所在地已改建成[[元山農業綜合大學|元山農業綜合大學]]<ref>{{cite web |title = Wonsan University of Agriculture |work = Flickr Photo Sharing, March 6, 2008 |url = http://www.flickr.com/photos/kernbeisser/2549943610/ |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |archive-date = 2015-12-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151209085918/https://www.flickr.com/photos/kernbeisser/2549943610/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。修院的殘存部分，包括聖堂、修院、宿舍等<ref>{{cite web |title = Former Tokwon Church & Seminary (Wonsan) |work = Wikimapia, 2011 |url = http://wikimapia.org/#lat=39.1943016&lon=127.3763251&z=18&l=5&m=b&show=/17306897/Former-Tokwon-Church-Seminary |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |archive-date = 2011-08-25 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/61CZ2O6Sc?url=http://wikimapia.org/#lat=39.1943016&lon=127.3763251&z=18&l=5&m=b&show=/17306897/Former-Tokwon-Church-Seminary |dead-url = no }}</ref>，可能被大學所佔用<ref>{{cite web|title = Main building of Wŏnsan Agricultural University, the former German Benedictine abbey Tŏgwon|work = Panoramio, October 5, 2008|url = http://www.panoramio.com/photo/14713538|accessdate = January 19, 2012|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130520154444/http://www.panoramio.com/photo/14713538|archive-date = 2013-05-20|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

1952年部分倖存的修士、修女在[[韓國|韓國]][[大邱|大邱]]附近[[倭館邑|倭館]]的建立了[[倭館隱修院|新的修道院]]<ref>{{cite web |title = St. Maurus and St. Placidus’ Abbey, Waegwan, South Korea |work = Inkama Abbey, April 2, 2011 |url = http://www.inkamana.org/ohio/waegwan.htm |accessdate = January 19, 2012 |archive-date = 2004-06-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040610124210/http://www.inkamana.org/ohio/waegwan.htm |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。隱修院的院長是會院區的[[宗座署理|宗座署理]]（2005年1月25日以前更兼任咸興教區的宗座署理，現任院牧為李炯雨）<ref>{{cite journal|journal = [[公教報|公教報]]
|date = 2006年2月5日
|issue = 3233
|title = 教廷委北韓宗座署理　結束本篤會管轄咸興 |url =
}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = Territorial Abbacy of Tokwon (덕원) |work = Giga-Catholic Information, January 15, 2012 |url = http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/tokw0.htm |accessdate = January 19, 2012 }}</ref>，但無法進入朝鮮。自1950年代起自治會院區以至整個朝鮮都已經沒有司鐸，以至天主教社群<ref>{{cite web |title = North Korean Martyrs, the first process for beatification gets underway |work = Asia News, May 25, 2007 |url = http://www.asianews.it/index.php?l=en&art=9368 |accessdate = January 10, 2012 |archive-date = 2012-09-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120925222950/http://www.asianews.it/index.php?l=en&art=9368 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = Korea, for a reconciliation between North and South |work = 30 days, March 2006 |url = http://www.30giorni.it/articoli_id_10278_l3.htm |accessdate = January 10, 2012 |archive-date = 2013-12-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131214235655/http://www.30giorni.it/articoli_id_10278_l3.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>。很多基督徒被囚禁於隱修院西北70[[公里|公里]]（43[[英里|英里]]）的[[耀德集中營|耀德集中營]]以及位於朝鮮其他地區的集中營<ref>{{cite web |title = North Korea: A case to answer, a call to act; section H. Persecution (p. 52) |work = Christian Solidarity Worldwide, 2007 |url = http://docs-eu.livesiteadmin.com/c8880e0f-f6ed-4585-8f09-4e4b6d11e698/north-korea-a-case-to-answer-a-call-to-act.pdf |accessdate = January 11, 2012 |archive-date = 2013-10-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131021204741/http://docs-eu.livesiteadmin.com/c8880e0f-f6ed-4585-8f09-4e4b6d11e698/north-korea-a-case-to-answer-a-call-to-act.pdf |dead-url = yes }}</ref>，因其信仰受到虐待和不人道待遇<ref>{{cite web |title = 50,000 Christians imprisoned in North Korea |work = Vatican Radio, April 15, 2011 |url = http://www.radiovaticana.org/IN2/articolo.asp?c=479048 |accessdate = January 11, 2012 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120908034043/http://www.radiovaticana.org/IN2/articolo.asp?c=479048 |archivedate = 2012年9月8日 }}</ref>。朝鮮的基督徒只能秘密地實踐其信仰，而且時刻面對被發現和處罰的危險<ref>{{cite web |title = Thank You Father Kim Il Sung (p. 40 - 42) |work = U.S. Commission on International Religious Freedom, November 2005 |url = http://www.davidrhawk.com/ThankYouFatherKimIlSung.pdf |accessdate = April 2, 2012 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120916014550/http://www.davidrhawk.com/ThankYouFatherKimIlSung.pdf |archivedate = 2012年9月16日 }}</ref>。

韓國教會在興建位於最接近[[朝韓非軍事區|朝韓非軍事區]]的[[坡州市|坡州市]]的[[懺悔贖罪堂_(坡州)|懺悔贖罪堂]]時，也參考了聖堂的內部設計。<ref>天主教亞洲通訊社，《邊境新教堂冀成為南北韓統一及福傳之所》，2013年7月5日。</ref>

